It is almost the most exciting time of year again, summer!
Our heroine, Nanami-chan, seems to be in a delightful mood!
She is completely absorbed in planning her summer vacation with her friends!
What you are saying and what is happening are completely different!
In the last episode, love bloomed.
Unfortunately, it also wilted as fast as it bloomed.
How will she recover from this heartbreak?
Hey, do you want to go to the beach, Momozono-san?
I would be thrilled to go.
Momozono-san, do not go toward the light!
You cannot expect much after having your confession rejected so spectacularly, though.
You still do not have your appetite back?
You have not even touched your lunch!
You will collapse if you do not!
You barely had any breakfast, and now you will not touch your lunch.
I keep trying to pick up the pieces of my heart, but then Tomoe just keeps popping up.
She still has not gotten over the rejection!
If you are not going to eat, then I will force-feed you!
I am the only one here who cannot control their feelings.
Meanwhile, Tomoe still has his composure.
There is just one difference now.
He will not even lay a finger on me.
You have got me right here!
Go to the beach with me!
You will feel much better once you run around for a bit.
That is nice and all, but do you two even have swimsuits?
What do you mean I cannot go?!
The beach and the ocean are breeding grounds for evil.
Humans might be fine, but I cannot possibly let a deity like you go alone!
Furthermore, I cannot enter the water, which is all the more reason for you to not go.
I will have my friends with me!
What good will those friends do you?
How about I take her for you, then?
Why did they have to tag along?!
No one's going to hit on us with you guys around!
No, they are not going to hit us!
Are you trying to act retarded?
Apparently Kei-chan broke up last night.
In the end Tomoe came with us...
I have got a bad feeling about this.
You look like a little kid with that.
I cannot swim without one, though.
Momozono-san, how is the swimsuit on you?
Thanks for letting me borrow it, Kei-chan!
This is the first time I have gotten to wear something like this!
I just did not want someone in a T-shirt swimming with me.
Why do not you go show it off to the guys?
Speaking of which, are they even going to swim today?
L-Let us get in the water!
You sure you do not want to show them?
They were not even supposed to be here today!
Why do I suddenly feel embarrassed?
I wonder if this is okay.
Does this look weird on me?
Do I... look good in it?
So why are you here, Tomoe-kun?
I could ask you the same.
Seriously, are not girls these days much too bold?
I cannot believe they would walk around with so much skin exposed.
I would not be surprised if some human males tried to eat them up.
I bet you are actually glad that you came along.
Though honestly, I did not think you would actually come along.
I know why you cannot get in the ocean.
I might hate your guts, but I have enough courtesy to not tell Nanami-chan.
Nanami-chan, mind if I come along?!
Look, I found this really pretty she will!
I wonder what cool things we will find!
He has some nerve putting his hands all over her while I cannot.
So the snake boy's going to swim?
You should come along too, Mikage-kun.
The problem is that if I get too close, Tomoe might notice me.
Rather, might I ask why you are wearing that oven of a coat here?
It is part of who I am.
If he learned that these past twenty years after abandoning him
that you were actually watching from afar...
Well, I would not be surprised if he straight-out killed you.
Tomoe would not do something like that.
He would dropkick me at best.
Tomoe-kun might look all cool, but I guess he does have his weaknesses.
I wonder if that human girl is one of them.
I am going for a swim.
As good of a friend as he is, I still cannot believe he is a deity.
I guess I will swim by myself since I am here anyway.
I am glad that you are feeling better.
You are looking extra scary today.
I tried finding her but I could not!
If my master makes a request, can I really say no?
It is time to go back.
I just got a mouthful of water.
Thank you for coming into the ocean.
You could not have made it any easier for me to find you.
I have been waiting for a long time for you to play in the big puddle, Tomoe.
I hope you have not forgotten the face of the King of the Dragons!
Sorry, but I cannot have bystanders getting in our way.
I have got some debts to collect.
Allow me to remind your stupid fox brain!
Exactly 526 years and 208 days ago, at 541 AM,
you came down to my lair at the bottom of the sea and slew the seven-headed dragon
and threeno, five great beasts of the ocean and a sea slug at the Noth Gate of the palace.
Then you destroyed the entire North Gate itself,
came to me, the King of Dragons, and gouged out my right eye.
You have got quite the debt, and I will make sure you pay back every last cent!
You will be worth more that way, anyway.
We were greatly impressed by your show of magnificence, King!
I have been planning this out for the past 526 years!
Let us go back to the Dragon Palace and celebrate!
What did you do to Tomoe!
Sorry, but that is as far as you go.
I will not let you go!
If I let go now, I might never see you again!
You are one persistent brat, you know?
I had my minions take him.
Besides, I was nice enough to drag you back here.
You can pay it off over time.
That fox owes me one hell of a debt.
What do you want me to do?
What can I do so you will let Tomoe out?
If you can give me the eye he took from me, I might spare his life.
My eyes are like seeds of power.
Those who manage to get their hands on one and eat it gain incredible power.
That fox took one of them 526 years ago.
In other words I, the Dragon King, had defeat permanently carved into my face.
If I can get the eye to you, you will give Tomoe back to me?
It is not as easy as you think.
I doubt you can get it now.
Promise me that if I get it, you will let Tomoe go!
I do not know what you are planning, but I promise.
I will hold onto the fox for two days.
There is one way I can save Tomoe.
I love how ice cream is so cold and sweet!
I have never had anything like this.
What the hell are you screwing around for?
Momozono and Tomoe are missing, and you decide to take your sweet time in the bath?!
Maybe we should call the police.
I think they will be fine.
Nanami-chan should be back by tomorrow.
I will sleep in the middle, okay?
I reserved this room for three women.
You and Tomoe can go sleep in a love hotel for all I care.
I am sorry I made you worry.
I told you she would be fine.
I need you to let me use your Route of Time.
I need to use it to go back into the past and get the eye from Tomoe.
If I can get the eye back, I can save Tomoe.
Nanami-chan, one of the girls told me that you like Tomoe.
T-T-T-That has nothing to do with the situation at
I am a bit jealous of him.
It is almost painful to watch him have a master that cares so deeply for him.
I always imagine how wonderful my life would be if Tomoe just disappeared.
I think this is what people call envy or jealously.
Nanami-chan, have you never thought that way about someone?
Tell me, how do I deal with these feelings?
I am asking so much of you...
But you are the only one I can count on!
When you put it that way, how can I say no?
It is a taboo to interfere with the past.
Then again, you are a deity so...
there is no one to stop you.
You actually brought that with you?
Yeah, ever since my home flooded, I have been carrying my valuables with me.
Last time I only brought your spirit back, but this time your whole body's going.
I can help a bit, but only as a guide.
The rest is up to you.
You are all I see in this light.
I will not fall in love with a human girl.
I-I suppose the fact that it is snowing means I have successfully returned to the past, but...
Are not you freezing in those clothes?
Do not you want this wind breaker?
I would not mind trading this for that Dragon King's Eye you have in you.
Mizuki, there was a woman just now.
That was a mermaid demon called Isohime.
It regularly ambushes humans around here.
Do not you have to look for Tomoe?
I have to look for him!
How dare you lay hands on my brethren!
Return the right eye of the Dragon King this instant!
I do not have time to deal with you.
The one I love is still stuck in the darkness.
Nanami and Mizuki have traveled into the past to retrieve the Dragon King's right eye!
But little did they expect to find Tomoe with a beautiful woman!
I wonder if Nanami and Tomoe can get back on good terms!
Next time, The Deity Goes to the Palace of the Dragon King!
